LibreWolf Browser Fetcher Bash Script
Produced by a citizen of the Nation of Flos Regium: https://flosregium.online
License: TNOFRS License (See License File)
Privacy Respecting Browser Startpage: https://historya.live/start/
=========================================

This bash script is designed to allow easy fetching of the latest LibreWolf AppImage, verify the integrity (sha256), and provide a portable lauch script for people who wish to use it in a portable manner.

How to use:
* Obtain the script package
* Read and agree to the short license
* Make the script(s) runable (chmod +x filename)
* The 1run.sh does the fetching
* The LibreWolf.AppImage.portable.sh does the portable launching
